@@ -1,5 +1,15 @@
 # Changelog
 
+## Unreleased
+
+- Add local `.dreamskin` MVP v1 import with strict ZIP limits, SHA-256 resource
+  checks, Ed25519/RFC 8785 verification, immutable version directories and
+  install/apply separation.
+- Register a per-user macOS handler for signed `.dreamskin` files and strict
+  `dreamskin://install` HTTPS links, with separate download and apply prompts.
+- Add macOS 14 CI coverage for complete `sips` image decoding, immutable
+  installation and the compatibility symlink used by existing theme switching.
+
 ## 1.1.1 — 2026-07-16
 
 ### 修复
